Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:01:00.21,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}natsukashii bamen hodoite koboshita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:05.67,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}eranda ketsui wo shimetsukeru paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:11.22,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}todokanai asu ni shizumeta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:17.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nigirishimeru kono te wo hirakeba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:25.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}furete shimau tou ni nageta kibou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:31.70,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}namida wo karashi mukau kono yami wo nuke
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:37.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}tsutsuganai mirai anata ga mitsumeteitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:43.17,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}yatto yatto tsukami kaketa hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:47.13,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}daremo nanimo iwanakute ii
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:58.56,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}subete no kotae wa koko ni chanto aru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:54.53,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}As cores se espalham até onde o olhar alcança,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:01:00.21,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}uma cena nostálgica se desenrola e se espalham.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:05.67,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Um paradoxo que confunde nossas decisões,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:11.22,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}afundado em um amanhã inalcançável.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:17.52,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Se eu abrir essa mão que seguro com força,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:25.61,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}poderei alcançar a esperança que abandonei há muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:31.70,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Enxugue suas lágrimas e siga em frente para romper esta escuridão.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:37.83,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Mesmo quando você olha para um futuro sem esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:43.17,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Eu finalmente, finalmente, comecei a entender a luz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:47.13,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Não é preciso dizer nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:58.56,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Porque todas as respostas estão bem aqui.
